    <abstract>
      <t>The BGP Monitoring Protocol (BMP) is designed to monitor BGP running
   status, such as BGP peer relationship establishment and termination
   and route updates.  This document provides a method of collecting the
   VPN label using BMP, as well as an implementation example.</t>
